{"id":2695,"date":"2024-08-30T12:32:50","date_gmt":"2024-08-30T12:32:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/?p=2695"},"modified":"2024-09-25T03:10:04","modified_gmt":"2024-09-25T03:10:04","slug":"thu-tuc-lam-lai-dau-tron-cong-ty-nhanh-chong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/thu-tuc-lam-lai-dau-tron-cong-ty-nhanh-chong\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n c\u00f4ng ty nhanh ch\u00f3ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c <a href=\"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/thu-tuc-lam-lai-dau-tron-cong-ty-nhanh-chong\/\">l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n c\u00f4ng ty<\/a> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1eeb khi Lu\u1eadt Doanh nghi\u1ec7p 2020 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ph\u00e1p l\u00fd v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n:<\/span><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ea5t d\u1ea5u: D\u1ea5u b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t do nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0 th\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c, b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u01b0 h\u1ecfng d\u1ea5u: M\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u b\u1ecb m\u1edd, n\u1ee9t, v\u1ee1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f4ng tin doanh nghi\u1ec7p: T\u00ean c\u00f4ng ty, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, m\u00e3 s\u1ed1 thu\u1ebf thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u c\u00f4ng ty khi b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c h\u1ecfng<\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng con d\u1ea5u b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t, h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u m\u1edbi. C\u00f3 2 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y 01\/07\/2015 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 con d\u1ea5u do c\u01a1 quan c\u00f4ng an c\u1ea5p:<\/span><\/h3>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p con d\u1ea5u b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t:<\/span><\/h4>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Ngay khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ea5t con d\u1ea5u, doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ngay cho c\u01a1 quan c\u00f4ng an n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea5p con d\u1ea5u. C\u01a1 quan, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t con d\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n cho c\u01a1 quan \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd m\u1eabu con d\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u01a1 quan c\u00f4ng an x\u00e3, ph\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n n\u01a1i x\u1ea3y ra m\u1ea5t con d\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng 2 ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u01a1 s\u1edf kh\u1eafc d\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m con d\u1ea5u m\u1edbi theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt Doanh nghi\u1ec7p 2020. Theo lu\u1eadt n\u00e0y, doanh nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c con d\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o m\u1eabu d\u1ea5u m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p con d\u1ea5u b\u1ecb h\u01b0, h\u1ecfng:<\/span><\/h4>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng cho c\u01a1 quan c\u00f4ng an n\u01a1i c\u1ea5p. H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb bao g\u1ed3m c\u00f4ng v\u0103n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u, b\u1ea3n sao \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd kinh doanh ho\u1eb7c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, b\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd m\u1eabu d\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Sau khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u, doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u01a1 s\u1edf kh\u1eafc d\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m con d\u1ea5u m\u1edbi theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt Doanh nghi\u1ec7p 2020.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote><p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/dia-chi-khac-dau-tron-khong-can-giay-to\/\">\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 Kh\u1eafc D\u1ea5u Tr\u00f2n Kh\u00f4ng C\u1ea7n Gi\u1ea5y T\u1edd<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp sau ng\u00e0y 01\/07\/2015 v\u1edbi con d\u1ea5u theo Lu\u1eadt Doanh nghi\u1ec7p 2014:<\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu con d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng, quy tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u01a1 s\u1edf kh\u1eafc d\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m con d\u1ea5u m\u1edbi theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt Doanh nghi\u1ec7p 2020 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o m\u1eabu d\u1ea5u m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u c\u0169 cho c\u01a1 quan \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd kinh doanh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u theo c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap doanh nghi\u1ec7p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ec sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u01a1 s\u1edf kh\u1eafc d\u1ea5u uy t\u00edn?<\/span><\/h2>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t: \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, b\u1ec1n m\u00e0u, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb nh\u00f2e m\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1eddi gian ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhanh: Gi\u00fap doanh nghi\u1ec7p ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh: \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi x\u1ea3y ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u00ean l\u00e0m d\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng: \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So s\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n, ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb: Sau khi l\u00e0m d\u1ea5u, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u01a1 s\u1edf cung c\u1ea5p h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n, ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote><p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/dong-dau-treo-chuan-nhat-dung-quy-dinh\/\">\u0110\u00f3ng d\u1ea5u treo chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang quy \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h2>\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i con d\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n c\u00f4ng ty uy t\u00edn<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/\"><strong>Kh\u1eafc d\u1ea5u l\u1ea5y li\u1ec1n Khada<\/strong><\/a> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u1eafc d\u1ea5u l\u1ea5y li\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong ng\u00e0nh, Khada cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m con d\u1ea5u s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, b\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n c\u00f4ng ty l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1eeb khi Lu\u1eadt Doanh nghi\u1ec7p 2020 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ph\u00e1p l\u00fd v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":2699,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2695","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2695","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2695"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2695\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2757,"href":"https:\/\/xuongkhacdauhn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/